snippet.title: Hello Girl (Visual Novel Trailer)
snippet.description:
Hello Girl is a visual novel created by IMO Team
Ana is a telephone operator. It used to be a respectable profession, but this is a world of progress, and the old must give way to the new.

Download for free for PC, Mac, and Linux
https://imoteam.itch.io/hello-girl

IMO Team is:
Merilynn F. Paisley
Mentha Nolana
Mara Welsley
Naja D'egoutter
and Kalibration

Follow IMO Team on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/imo_team

Support IMO Team on Ko-fi:
https://ko-fi.com/imo_team
